=== .claude/commands/deploy.md ===
---
type: command
version: 1.0.0
description: Deploy the service.
---

Run the deploy pipeline for the named environment.

=== .claude/rules/deep-review.md ===
Perform a deep architectural review when invoked.

=== .claude/rules/tabs-always.md ===
Indent with tabs, not spaces.

=== .claude/rules/ts-auto.md ===
Prefer interfaces over type aliases.

=== .claude/rules/ts-glob.md ===
---
paths:
  - "*.ts"
  - "*.tsx"
---

Enable strict type-checking in TypeScript files.

=== .claude/settings.json ===
{
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "command": "./scripts/guard.sh",
            "type": "command"
          }
        ],
        "x-podium-id": "team/guard"
      }
    ],
    "Stop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "command": "echo done",
            "type": "command"
          }
        ],
        "x-podium-id": "team/notify"
      }
    ]
  }
}

